# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share this in the checkin or not?
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if platform is not same, might be better to exclude Pipfile.lock.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   According to poetry documentation, it is recommended to include poetry.lock in version control.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   According to pdm documentation, it is recommended to include pdm.lock in version control.
# pdm.lock

